to take on a project this size.

45
00:03:39.678 --> 00:03:41.554
If it were easy.
we wouldn't take it.

46
00:03:41.555 --> 00:03:43.765
- I would.
- I know you would!

47
00:03:43.766 --> 00:03:45.224
Of course I would.

48
00:03:45.225 --> 00:03:46.727
- Dad?
- Come in!

49
00:03:48.437 --> 00:03:51.856
