- Me? No way.

54
00:04:04.161 --> 00:04:05.536
I've got a tunnel to build.

55
00:04:05.537 --> 00:04:07.957
Dalal will kick me out!

56
00:04:09.541 --> 00:04:12.002
I think
this little rascal here...

57
00:04:14.046 --> 00:04:15.130
looks like a...

58
