59
00:04:17.591 --> 00:04:18.591
Let me see.

60
00:04:18.592 --> 00:04:19.927
I know how to do it.

61
00:05:23.449 --> 00:05:25.324
PIMPÃO: Hold on. guys.

62
00:05:25.325 --> 00:05:26.492
What's that?

63
00:05:26.493 --> 00:05:28.162
Kill the joint. Reyna.

64
00:05:31.081 --> 00:05:33.166
